<law type="statute"><section id="id210"><amendatorysection chaptername="Livestock" statutenumber="54-179.05"><bookinfo>Revised Statutes Cumulative Supplement, 2026</bookinfo><statuteno>54-179.05</statuteno><catchline>Dairy heifer development facility, defined.</catchline><para>Dairy heifer development facility means a facility that specializes in raising and managing dairy heifers until such dairy heifers are ready for breeding or calving.</para></amendatorysection></section><source><para>Laws 2026, LB1187, &#167; 6. </para><operativedate>July 18, 2026</operativedate></source></law>
